8ecd1679390.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Friday, November 14, 2025 7:42 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-11-14 7:42 a.m.", "text": "Aaah good thinking", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Aaah good thinking</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1438872076093100102", "author": "Jon 🇬🇧", "author_handle": "d_frag69", "user_id": "331738952195244034", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/331738952195244034/351a93740e8df7a83414720c72d10abf.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Friday, November 14, 2025 7:43 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-11-14 7:43 a.m.", "text": "I'm not sure it's a bad decision for them. Essentially has central heating", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>I&#39;m not sure it&#39;s a bad decision for them.  Essentially has central heating</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=rofl><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=🤣 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f923.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1438879658056618025", "author": "Scarecrow", "author_handle": "superstarchar", "user_id": "144009793265336320", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/144009793265336320/3483db2a9d91c5cacc8268ecd1679390.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Friday, November 14, 2025 8:14 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-11-14 8:14 a.m.", "text": "Maybe not a bad decision for them, but I don’t think your board will appreciate the feathers and poop additions that come with feathered friends", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Maybe not a bad decision for them, but I don’t think your board will appreciate the feathers and poop additions that come with feathered friends <img\n    loading=\"lazy\"\n    class=\"chatlog__emoji \"\n    alt=\"😂\"\n    title=\"joy\"\n    src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f602.svg\"></span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=joy><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=😂 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f602.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1438905951532093542", "author": "PoorSignal", "author_handle": "psidnell", "user_id": "828549897393143808", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/828549897393143808/12a1f0928739bd89d020469c18eea904.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Friday, November 14, 2025 9:58 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-11-14 9:58 a.m.", "text": "I’m imagining a tiny Yagi that pops out of the hole on the hour like a cuckoo clock.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>I’m imagining a tiny Yagi that pops out of the hole on the hour like a cuckoo clock.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=rofl><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=🤣 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f923.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "<div class=chatlog__reply><img class=chatlog__reply-avatar src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/331738952195244034/351a93740e8df7a83414720c72d10abf.png?size=512\" alt=Avatar loading=lazy><div class=chatlog__reply-author title=d_frag69>Jon 🇬🇧</div><div class=chatlog__reply-content><span class=chatlog__reply-link onclick